headline: Ispire Technology Inc. (ISPR) Reports Q4 Loss, Lags Revenue Estimates
summary: Ispire Technology Inc. (ISPR) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -85.71% and -10.10%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
